---
title: Rosemary Ricotta Flatbread with Roasted Grapes
description: We love the combination of sweet & salty, and this dish really hits a home-run. Creamy ricotta, sautéed leeks, and peppery arugula are complimented by roasted grapes; a sweet touch to this rustic flatbread.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54d222906ced6e7e1b8b4568.jpg
